title: ITG looking for D2+ jungle

embed.description: Application to be the jungler for Invisible Threat Gaming.

body:
Hey everyone! 

ITG is searching for a D2+ jungler. We want a motivated individual who is looking to play professionally. Our aim is to qualify for OCS through the split 2 OOL. 

Our team has been together for one month, but we are currently in need of a new jg player

Please fill out the google form to apply! We will email you with tryout dates and further information! 

Thank you :)
